<p><strong>Medium construct, lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 21 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 112 (15d8+45)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

